Peter Jones ya yi 'karya' bayan Holly Willoughby ta soke yarjejeniyar £11-million
Dan wasan kwallon kafa na  Dragons Peter Jones ya yi 'fushi' bayan da mai gabatar da gidan talabijin Holly Willoughby ta soke yarjejeniyar £11-million da ta yi da kamfanin salon rayuwarsa domin mayar da hankali kan sabbin kwangilolinta da  Marks and Spencer da ITV
Willoughby ba shi da lokaci don kamfanin kayan gida da kayan haɗi, Truly.
An kwatanta kasuwancin na biyu da Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop.
Mai gabatar da shirin This Morning, mai shekara 37, ta bayyana a shafin Instagram ta sanar da cewa za ta tafi.
Holly Willoughby ta bar dan wasan Dragons Peter Jones cikin fushi saboda an soke shi daga kasancewa wani ɓangare na kasuwancin su na babban kuɗi na salon rayuwa a minti na ƙarshe - don mayar da hankali kan manyan kwangilarsa tare da Marks & Spencer da ITV.
Majiyoyi sun ce Jones ya yi "fushi sosai" lokacin da shahararren dan wasan talabijin ya yarda a wani taro mai cike da tashin hankali a ranar Talata a hedkwatar kasuwancinsa na Marlow, Buckinghamshire, cewa sabbin yarjejeniyoyinsa - masu darajar har zuwa £1.5m - sun nuna cewa ba ta da isasshen lokaci don yin alkawarin kamfanin su na kayayyakin gida da kayan haɗi, Truly.
An kwatanta kasuwancin da Gwyneth Paltrow Goop's firm kuma an yi imanin zai ninka darajar Willoughby ta £11m.
Kamar yadda Willoughby, mai shekara 37, ta bayyana a Instagram don sanar da cewa za ta bar Truly, Jones ya bar Burtaniya kuma ya tafi ɗayan ƙauyukansa na sirri.
Wani majiya ya ce: "Gaskiya ita ce ainihin abin da Holly ta fi so.
Wannan zai zama makomar ta na dogon lokaci da za ta cika shekaru da yawa masu zuwa.
Ƙudurinta na barin ya ba kowa mamaki.
Babu wanda ya iya gaskata abin da ke faruwa a ranar Talata, ƙaddamarwa ta kusan zuwa.
Akwai kantin sayar da kayayyaki a hedkwatar Marlow da ke shirye don sayarwa".
Masana sun yi imanin cewa barin mai gabatar da shirin This Morning, wanda ke cikin manyan masu kawo riba a Burtaniya, na iya haifar da asarar miliyoyin kuɗi ga kamfanin saboda babban jarin da aka yi a kan kayayyaki daga kayan aiki da kyandir zuwa tufafi da kayayyakin gida, da kuma yiwuwar ƙarin jinkiri har zuwa ƙaddamar da shi.
Kuma zai iya nufin ƙarshen abokantaka mai daɗewa.
Uwar 'ya'ya uku, Willoughby da mijinta Dan Baldwin sun kasance abokai na Jones da matarsa Tara Capp na tsawon shekaru goma.
Willoughby ta tsayar da Truly tare da Capp a cikin 2016 kuma Jones, 52, ya shiga tare da su a matsayin shugaban zartarwa a watan Maris.
Ma'aurata suna tafiya tare kuma Jones yana da kashi 40 cikin ɗari na kamfanin samar da talabijin na Baldwin.
Willoughby za ta zama jakadan kamfanin M&S kuma za ta maye gurbin Ant McPartlin a matsayin mai gabatar da shirin I'm A Celebrity na ITV.
A daren jiya, wata majiya da ke kusa da Jones ta ce "Ba mu da wata ma'ana game da harkokin tattalin arzikinsa".
