Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli jawabin Brett Kavanaugh
Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidar ranar Alhamis ta mai neman kujerar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh da matar da suka zargi da aikata laifin cin zarafin da ake zargin ya faru ne a shekarun 1980s, Christine Blasey Ford, a tashoshin talabijin shida.
A halin yanzu, yakin siyasa ya ci gaba, inda masu watsa shirye-shirye suka katse shirye-shiryen yau da kullun tare da mummunan labari na minti na ƙarshe a ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya tsara don FBI don gudanar da binciken mako guda na tuhumar.
