Kavanaugh, a cikin shaidar da ya bayar da sha'awa, ya ce yana da tabbacin cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Wataƙila sama da mutane miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli bidiyon kamar yadda Nielsen ta ruwaito a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin yana ƙididdige matsakaicin yawan masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a nan take aka samu alkaluman ga sauran hanyoyin sadarwa da suka nuna su ba, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Kuma Nielsen yawanci yana da wahalar ƙididdige yawan masu kallo daga ofisoshi.
Don sanya wannan a cikin hangen nesa, yana da girman masu sauraro kamar na wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ko na Academy Awards.
Tashar Fox News Channel, wadda masu ra'ayinta suka goyi bayan nadin Kavanaugh, ta yi fice a kan dukkan tashoshi da matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a lokacin zaman da ya dauki tsawon yini guda, in ji Nielsen.
ABC na nan a bayansa da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS tana da miliyan 3.1 da NBC tana da miliyan 2.94 da MSNBC tana da miliyan 2.89 da CNN tana da miliyan 2.52, in ji Nielsen.
Sha'awa ta kasance mai ƙarfi bayan taron.
Flake shi ne babban dan wasan wasan na ranar Juma'a.
Bayan da ofishin jam'iyyar Republican mai tsaka-tsakin ya fitar da sanarwa cewa zai kada kuri'a a kan Kavanaugh, masu zanga-zangar sun kama shi a kyamarorin CNN da CBS a safiyar Juma'a suna ihu da shi yayin da yake kokarin hawa lif don taron kwamitin shari'a.
