A ranar Lahadi, LeBron zai buga wasan farko da Lakers a San Diego
'Yan wasan LeBron James sun yi farin ciki da ganin shi ya fara buga wasan Los Angeles Lakers.
Kocin Lakers Luke Walton ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na kakar wasa ta 2019 a ranar Lahadi da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Amma adadin mintuna da za a yi wasa da su har yanzu ba a tantance su ba.
"Za a yi sama da ɗaya kuma ƙasa da 48", in ji Walton a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Dan jaridar Lakers Mike Trudell ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa, mai yiwuwa James zai buga wasa na iyakance na minti biyar.
Bayan zaman atisayen da aka yi a farkon makon, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na shirya wasannin 6 na gasar kafin a fara kakar wasa ta Lakers.
"A wannan mataki na aikina, ba na bukatar wasannin kafin kakar wasa don in shirya kaina", in ji shi.
Taron Trump a West Virginia, Tashar Youtube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara wani gangamin yakin neman zabe a daren yau a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin tarurrukan Trump biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da aka dakatar da kuri'ar tabbatar da zabensa na cike wa babban kotun da ke kan kujerar, Trump na son gina goyon baya ga zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar hatsarin rasa iko da majalisa a lokacin da za a kada kuri'ar a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia zai gudana kuma yaya za ka iya ganin sa a intanet?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia da karfe 7 na yammacin yau, Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon zanga-zangar Trump a West Virginia a kan layi ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube a ƙasa.
Trump zai yi jawabi ne a wannan makon a gaban kotun koli na kasar nan, wanda ya zabi Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi taurin kai saboda zargin da ake yi masa na lalata da 'yan mata, inda aka dakatar da zaben amincewa da shi na tsawon mako guda, yayin da ake gudanar da bincike kan FBI.
Amma babban dalilin wannan zanga-zangar shi ne don taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar zaben na watan Nuwamba su samu ci gaba.
Kamfanin yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump ya ce, wadannan tarurruka biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, na nufin karfafawa masu aikin agaji da masu goyon baya a yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, in ji Reuters.
"Sarrafawa a majalisa na da muhimmanci sosai ga wannan ajanda cewa shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama yayin da muke gab da lokacin kamfen", in ji wani mai magana da yawun yakin neman zaben Trump wanda ya ki bayyana sunansa.
An shirya taron ne a filin wasa na Wesbanco a Wheeling, kuma za a iya samun masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma samun rahoto daga kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai kai ziyara karo na biyu a watan jiya a jihar West Virginia, jihar da ta lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar Sanatan Jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke faduwa a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo ne don ya kara masa ƙarfi a cikin binciken ba", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Kofin Ryder na 2018: Team USA sun ƙudura niyyar kada su yi kasa a gwiwa yayin da suke neman takarar a wasannin na ranar Lahadi
Bayan zaman guda uku, wasannin hudu na yammacin ranar Asabar na iya zama daidai abin da ake bukata a gasar Ryder.
Dandalin motsa jiki na lokaci abu ne na wasa da aka kirkira amma wanda 'yan wasa suka yi imani da shi, kuma ba haka ba ne a irin wannan gasa.
To, ina ne suke cewa lokaci ya yi?
"Sun yi nasara da maki shida kuma yanzu sun kai na hudu, don haka ina ganin suna kawo wannan a matsayin wani abu na ci gaba", in ji Jordan Spieth yayin da ya tashi a rana.
Turai tana da fa'ida, ba shakka, maki huɗu a gaba tare da sauran goma sha biyu da za a buga.
'Yan Amurkan, in ji Spieth, suna jin cewa suna da 'yan cikas kuma suna da abin karfafa gwiwa, ba kalla irin na Spieth da Justin Thomas da suka yi wasa tare duk rana ba kuma kowannensu yana alfahari da maki uku daga hudu.
Spieth ya kasance daidai daga tee zuwa kore kuma yana jagorantar da misali.
Wannan murna ta farin ciki ta kara ƙaruwa yayin da ya ci gaba da zagayen, inda ya yi wani muhimmin bugun da ya kawo wasan na huɗu daidai lokacin da shi da Thomas suka kasance biyu a baya.
Wasan da ya ci su a kan 15 ya samu karbuwa daga irin wannan kuka, irin wanda ke gaya maka cewa ya yi imani da cewa har yanzu akwai tawagar Amurka.
"Ya kamata ka shiga cikin zurfin kuma ka damu game da wasan ka", in ji Spieth.
Wannan shi ne abin da ya rage ga kowane daga cikin wadannan 'yan wasan a yanzu.
Rami 18 don yin alama.
'Yan wasa guda da suka fi Spieth da Thomas a cikin kwanaki biyu da suka gabata sune Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, tarihin Ryder Cup da ba a iya musantawa.
