Wannan gudu, da kuma yadda suke ganin kamar suna motsawa zuwa da kuma daga cikin wannan taro mai cike da farin ciki ya tabbatar da cewa su ne 'yan wasan da ke ba da ƙalubalen ranar Lahadi, kuma babu wani ɗan wasa da ya fi shahara wajen samun nasara a Turai yayin da rana ta faɗi a kan Le Golf National fiye da Fleetwood ko Molinari.
Zai fi kyau su yi hakan a lokaci ɗaya a kan ramuka dabam dabam.
Amma muna magana ne game da ɗaukakar Turai da ta fara.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi saurin samun nasara daga Sergio Garcia, jarumin wasan kwallon kafa na safe, lokacin da aka sanya su a kan Alex Noren.
Bogey da biyu doubles a kan tara na gaba sun shigar da Mutanen Espanya da Sweden a cikin rami wanda ba su taɓa isa kusa da fita ba.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai taimake ka ka fita daga cikin ramin.
Kwallan hudu da foursomes suna da ban sha'awa sosai don a gan su da kyau saboda hulɗar da ke tsakanin takwarorinsu, shawarwarin da suke bayarwa, shawarwarin da ba sa bayarwa da kuma yadda za a iya canza dabarun a cikin sakan.
Turai ta fi kyau a matsayin ta, saboda haka ta zo da kyau a gabanta a ranar karshe, amma wannan zaman na hudu ya kuma nuna cewa Team USA na da ƙudurin da wasu, musamman na Amurka, suka yi shakku a kai.
Turai ta yi nasara da 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar cin kofin Ryder
Turai za ta yi nasara a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup bayan ta yi nasara a wasannin hudu da hudu na ranar Asabar da ci 10-6 a kan Amurka.
Abokan motsa jiki Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun yi ƙoƙari tare da nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods wanda ya sami matsala don ɗaukar ƙimar su gaba ɗaya a cikin Le Golf National ta maki huɗu.
Ƙungiyar Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, wadda ta yi niyyar riƙe kofin da ta yi hasara a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta mamaye ƙungiyar Amurka da ta yi rashin nasara a wasan kwallon kafa na safe, wadda ta ci 3-1.
Amurka ta ba da ƙarin juriya a cikin foursomes, ta ci wasanni biyu, amma ba ta iya isa ga bambancin ƙimar ba.
Jam'iyyar Jim Furyk ta bukaci maki takwas daga wasanni 12 da dan wasa daya ya buga a ranar Lahadi domin rike kofin.
Fleetwood shine farkon dan Turai na kakar wasa da ya ci maki hudu a jere yayin da shi da Molinari, wanda aka yi wa lakabi da "Molliwood" bayan karshen mako mai kayatarwa, su ne kawai na biyu da suka ci maki hudu a wasannin farko na gasar Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun mamaye Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan kwallon hudu, sai suka yi aiki mai kyau don cinye Woods da sabon dan wasan Amurka na kakar wasa Bryson Dechambeau da ci 5 da 4.
Woods, wanda ya sha wahala a wasanni biyu na ranar Asabar, ya nuna wasu lokutan daukaka amma yanzu ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasansa 29 a wasan kwallon hudu da hudu da bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda ya yi nasara a wasan kwallon kafa na safe, ya koma dan wasan Henrik Stenson a wasan kwallon kafa na hudu domin ya ci Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka da 2 da 1 - wadanda ke matsayi na farko da na uku a duniya.
Amma ba abin da Turai ta yi tsammani ba ne a ranar farin ciki, da wani ɗan rawa a Paris.
Jordan Spieth, wanda ya lashe gasar sau uku, da Justin Thomas sun kafa iyakar 'yan Amurka da maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun sami nasara mai karfin gwiwa na 2&1 akan Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter na Spain a cikin hudu kuma sun dawo daga baya don cin Poulter da Rory McIlroy da 4&3 a cikin hudu bayan sun rasa ramuka biyu na buɗewa.
Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder ta samu tawagar da ta dawo daga ragar maki hudu a lokacin da ta shiga gasar guda, duk da cewa masu rike da gasar Furyk na bukatar a yi musu wasa don su rike kofin.
