Gerrard ya amsa a kan birki ta hanyar maye gurbin Coulibaly da Ryan Kent kuma canjin ya kusan ba da tasiri nan take yayin da mai tsaron ya harba a Morelos amma Kelly mai ban sha'awa ya gudu daga layinsa don toshewa.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da jan hankalin masu ziyara don yin daidai irin wasan da suke so, tare da Lithgow da Halkett suna cin dogon ball bayan dogon ball.
Holt ya iya fadada matsayinsa a gaba a matakai na karshe amma McGregor ya tsaya ya yi watsi da Jacobs kafin Lithgow ta shiga cikin budewa.
Mai maye gurbin Rangers Glenn Middleton ya sake yin kira a baya don fanni yayin da yake jayayya da Jacobs amma kuma Thomson ya kalli gefe.
