Tauraruwar Game of Thrones Kit Harington ta yi magana game da lalata mai guba
Kit Harington sananne ne ga rawar da ya taka a matsayin mai jan takobi kamar Jon Snow a cikin HBO's Game of Thrones.
Amma dan wasan mai shekaru 31 ya yi magana game da halin jarumin macho, yana mai cewa irin wadannan ayyuka a kan allo na nufin cewa matasa sukan ji cewa dole ne su kasance masu tashin hankali domin a girmama su.
Da yake magana da The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce ya yi imanin cewa wani abu ya ɓace kuma yana da shakku kan yadda za a magance matsalar ƙarancin maza a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri jarumar wasan sa na Game of Thrones Rose Leslie, mai shekaru 31 kuma, ya yarda cewa yana da 'babban sha'awa' wajen magance lamarin.
"Ni kaina, ina jin ina da sha'awar gaske, a yanzu - inda muka tafi ba daidai ba game da maza", in ji shi.
Me muke koya wa maza yayin da suke girma, dangane da matsalar da muke da ita yanzu?
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya kasance da wani ɓangare na alhakin ƙaruwar ƙwayoyin cuta ta hanyar halayensa masu mazanci.
Ya ci gaba: "Mecece dabi'a kuma menene koyarwa?"
