Daga watan Nuwamba Kit zai bayyana a sabon samar da Sam Shepard na True West wanda shine labarin wani mai samar da fina-finai da dan uwansa, wanda ya kasance mai zamba.
A kwanan nan, ɗan wasan ya bayyana cewa ya yi tunanin saduwa da matarsa Rose shine mafi kyawun abin da ya fito daga Game of Thrones.
"Na sadu da matata a wannan shirin, don haka ta wannan hanyar na ba ni iyalina na gaba, da rayuwata daga yanzu", in ji shi.
