HIV/Aids: China ta ba da rahoton ƙaruwar 14% na sababbin cututtuka
Kasar Sin ta sanar da karuwar kashi 14% na yawan 'yan kasarta da ke rayuwa da cutar HIV da AIDS.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne ke fama da cutar a kasar, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kawai an ba da rahoton sabbin shari'o'i kusan 40,000.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun kasance ta hanyar jinsi, wanda ke nuna canji daga baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin sakamakon kamuwa da jini.
