Wakilin Amurka Maxine Waters a ranar Asabar ta yi tir da zargin cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya sanya bayanan sirri na  uku na 'yan majalisar dattijai na Republican a shafukan Wikipedia na 'yan majalisa.
'Yan Democrat na Los Angeles sun tabbatar da cewa ana yada wannan ikirarin ne ta hanyar masana da kuma shafukan yanar gizo na 'yancin-kai.
Waters ta ce a cikin wata sanarwa a shafin Twitter, "ƙarya, ƙarya da kuma ƙarin ƙarya daga mai kira".
Bayanan da aka ce sun hada da adiresoshin gida da lambobin waya na Sanatocin Amurka Lindsey Graham na South Carolina, da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, dukansu na Utah.
Bayanan sun bayyana a intanet a ranar Alhamis, wanda wani ba a san shi ba ya wallafa a kan Capitol Hill a lokacin da aka yi zaman majalisar dattawa game da zargin cin zarafin da aka yi wa wanda ya zabi kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh.
An yi wannan sanarwar ne bayan da 'yan majalisar uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
