Ra'ayin Johnny English Strikes Again - Rowan Atkinson, wani ɗan leƙen asiri da ba shi da kyau
Ya zama al'ada a yanzu a nemi ma'anar Brexit a cikin kowane sabon fim da hangen nesa na Burtaniya kuma wannan ya zama mai amfani ga dawowar fim ɗin kwaikwayon wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English - wanda aka fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma aka sake farfado da shi a 2011 tare da Johnny English Reborn.
Irin wannan abin dariya game da batun  yadda muke da rashin gaskiya, zai zama damar  sabon fitarwa na ƙasar?
A kowane hali, Johnny English mai banƙyama da manyan idanu da kuma sassan fuskarsa da ke motsawa ba tare da saba ba ya sami lasisi na biyu don yin komai ba daidai ba - wannan sunan ya nuna fiye da komai cewa yana da zane-zane mai ban dariya wanda aka tsara don yankunan masu zuwa cinema waɗanda ba su magana da Ingilishi ba.
Hakika shi dan leken asiri ne wanda duk da irin wannan son zuciya da kuma irin wannan salon salon ya na da ɗan Clouseau, da ɗan Mr Bean, da kuma ɗan mutumin da ya ba da rawa guda ɗaya ga waƙar wasan kwaikwayo na Chariots of Fire a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta 2012 a London.
Hakanan asalinsa ya dogara ne akan matafiyi da kuma mutum mai ban mamaki wanda Atkinson ya taɓa yin sa a cikin tallan Barclaycard TV, wanda yanzu ya manta, bayan ya bar kaos a bayansa.
Akwai wani abu mai kyau ko biyu a cikin wannan fitowar ta ƙarshe ta JE.
Na ji daɗin lokacin da Johnny English ya hau zuwa jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu da tufafinsa na dā da kuma ƙyallen da aka saka masa da kwalkwali.
Kyautar Atkinson ga wasan kwaikwayo na zahiri yana bayyane, amma abin dariya yana jin dadi sosai kuma ya fi ban mamaki, musamman tunda alamun fim kamar 007 da Mission Impossible kansu suna ba da wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin kayan haɗi.
Abin dariya yana jin kamar an mai da hankali ne ga yara maimakon manya, kuma a wurina abubuwan ban dariya na Johnny English ba su da ƙira da kuma ma'ana kamar abin dariya na fim ɗin Atkinson a cikin mutumin Bean.
