Turanci da Bough sun fara tafiyarsu ta yin wasan kwaikwayo: suna yin ado a matsayin masu watsa labarai, suna ƙona gidan cin abinci na Faransa, suna haifar da rikici don hawa jirgin ruwan Volta mai tsada; kuma Turanci ya fara rikici gaba ɗaya yayin da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da abubuwan da ke cikin Virtual Reality don ya san kansa da cikin gidan Volta.
