Menene bikin Global Citizen kuma ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar mai zuwa, New York za ta karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen, wani biki na shekara-shekara na kiɗa wanda ke da jerin taurari masu tasowa da kuma wata manufa mai ban mamaki; kawo ƙarshen talauci a duniya.
Yanzu, a shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen zai ga dubun dubatan mutane suna zuwa babban lawn na Central Park ba wai kawai don jin daɗin masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma kuma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar taron da za a kawo ƙarshen matsanancin talauci ta 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012, wani bangare ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ce ta wakilci da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke fafutukar yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta zuwa taron (sai dai idan na yarda in biya tikitin VIP), masu halartar za su kammala jerin ayyuka, ko kuma su yi ayyuka kamar su ba da kai, aika imel ga wani shugaban duniya, yin kira ko kuma wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana don taimakawa wayar da kan jama'a game da burinsu na kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya Global Citizen ya yi nasara a cikin shekaru 12 da suka rage don cimma burin sa?
Shin ra'ayin cewa mutane za su sami kyauta ta hanyar yin wasa kyauta hanya ce ta gaske ta shawo kan mutane su nemi a yi musu kira, ko kuwa wani abu ne da ake kira "klictivism" - mutane suna jin cewa suna yin canji ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takarda ta yanar gizo ko aika tweets?
Tun daga 2011, Global Citizen ta ce ta yi rajistar sama da ayyuka miliyan 19 daga masu goyon bayanta, wadanda ke taimakawa a fannoni daban-daban.
Ya ce wadannan ayyuka sun taimaka wajen karfafawa shugabannin duniya gwiwa su sanar da alkawura da manufofi da suka kai dala biliyan 37 da ake sa ran za su shafi rayuwar sama da mutane biliyan 2.25 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta yi alkawarin yin alkawari 390 da kuma sanarwar daga cikin hannayenta, aƙalla dala biliyan 10 daga cikinsu an riga an biya ko an tara.
Ƙungiyar ta kimanta cewa, asusun tsaro ya yi tasiri kai tsaye a kan kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawuran sun hada da The Power of Nutrition, wata kungiya mai kafa kasar Birtaniya na masu zuba jari da masu aiwatar da ayyuka da ke da alhakin taimaka wa yara su girma zuwa ga cikakkiyar damar su, tare da alkawarin samar wa Rwanda da dala miliyan 35 domin taimakawa wajen kawo karshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar bayan karbar tweets sama da 4,700 daga Global Citizens.
Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da tallafi, gwamnatocin kasa, da kuma 'Yan Kasa na Duniya kamar ku, za mu iya sanya rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a tarihinmu, in ji jakadan The Power of Nutrition Tracey Ullman ga jama'a a wani taron kai tsaye a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan an dauki mataki sama da 5,000 na kira ga Burtaniya da ta inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga mata da yara, gwamnatin ta sanar da kudade ga wani shiri, the Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai mata da yara mata miliyan 5 da ke da matsalar abinci mai gina jiki.
A amsa ga ɗaya daga cikin tambayoyin da ake yawan yi a shafinsa na yanar gizo, ya ce: "Me ya sa kake ganin za mu iya kawar da talauci?
Global Citizen ya amsa: Za ta kasance doguwar tafiya mai wuya - wani lokacin za mu yi tuntuɓe kuma mu kasa.
Amma, kamar manyan ƙungiyoyin kare hakkin jama'a da na nuna wariyar launin fata, za mu yi nasara, domin muna da ƙarfi idan muka haɗa kai.
Janet Jackson, the Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Monáe na daga cikin masu fasahar da za su bayyana a taron na wannan shekara a New York, wanda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su gabatar.
Amurka na amfani da rundunar sojin ruwan don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - Sakataren Cikin Gida
"Idan ya zama dole", Washington na iya yin amfani da rundunar sojan ruwanta don hana makamashin Rasha shiga kasuwannin, ciki har da Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ta nakalto.
Zinke ya yi zargin cewa, ci gaban Rasha a Syria - musamman, inda take aiki a bisa gayyatar gwamnati mai halal - ya zama hujja don gano sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
Ina ganin dalilin da ya sa suke a Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne domin suna son yin ciniki a kan makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a Gabashin Turai, kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma, a cewar jami'in, akwai hanyoyin da za a bi wajen magance wannan.
"Amurka tana da ikon, tare da rundunar jiragen ruwanta, ta tabbatar da bude hanyoyin teku, kuma, idan ya zama dole, ta toshe su, ta tabbatar da cewa makamashin su bai kai kasuwa ba", in ji shi.
Zinke yana magana ne ga masu halartar taron da kungiyar Consumers Energy Alliance ta shirya, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta mai zaman kanta da ke da'awar cewa ita ce 'muryar masu amfani da makamashi' a Amurka.
Ya ci gaba da kwatanta hanyoyin Washington wajen magance Rasha da Iran, inda ya lura cewa sun yi kama.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziƙi akan Iran da Rasha shine, a mafi yawan lokuta, kayan aiki da maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yana mai magana da Rasha a matsayin "wani mutum mai ƙarfi" tare da tattalin arziƙin da ya dogara da man fetur.
Kalaman na zuwa ne yayin da gwamnatin Trump ke kan aikin bunkasa fitar da iskar gas dinta zuwa Turai, ta maye gurbin Rasha, mai rahusa ga masu amfani da Turai.
Don wannan, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump da kansa, suna kokarin tura Jamus ta fice daga aikin samar da iskar gas mai suna "Nord Stream 2", wanda a cewar Trump, ya sanya Berlin ta zama "gidan wuta" ga Moscow.
Moscow ta sha jaddada cewa, aikin gas mai karfin dala biliyan 11 na Nord Stream 2, wanda ake sa ran zai ninka karfin aikin gas na yanzu zuwa murabba'in mita biliyan 110, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Kremlin ya yi jayayya cewa tsananin adawar da Washington ke yi wa aikin ya samo asali ne daga dalilai na tattalin arziki kuma misali ne na rashin adalci.
"Na yi imanin cewa muna da ra'ayi iri daya cewa makamashi ba zai iya zama kayan aiki don matsa lamba ba kuma ya kamata masu amfani su sami damar zaɓar masu samarwa", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Aleksandr Novak bayan ganawa da Sakataren Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Matsayin Amurka ya jawo hankulan Jamus, wacce ta sake tabbatar da jajircewarta ga aikin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, Federation of German Industries (BDI), ta gayyaci Amurka da ta yi watsi da manufofin makamashi na Turai da yarjejeniyar biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala idan wata kasa ta uku ta tsoma baki a samar da wutar lantarki", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban kungiyar masana'antun Jamus (BDI) bayan ganawar da aka yi kwanan nan tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren Za Ta Yi Binciken Yadda Za Ta Yi Tsayin Gwiwa A 2020 In Ji Sanatan Massachusetts
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta yi la'akari sosai idan za ta tsaya takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben tsakiyar shekara.
A wani taron majalisar a Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ya tabbatar da cewa yana tunanin fita.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma hakan ya hada da mace a matsayi mafi girma", in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
Bayan 6 ga Nuwamba, zan yi la'akari sosai idan na tsaya takarar shugaban kasa.
Warren ta yi tsokaci kan shugaba Donald Trump a taron majalisar, inda ta ce yana kai kasar nan cikin mummunan yanayi.
"Ina matukar damuwa game da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyarmu", in ji ta.
Warren ta yi magana kai tsaye a kan Trump da kuma nadin da ya yi wa Brett Kavanaugh a matsayin babban alkalin kotun.
A cikin wata tweet a ranar Juma'a, Warren ta ce "a zahiri muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin zabe".
Duk da haka, wani zabe da ya fito a ranar Alhamis, ya nuna cewa mafiya yawan 'yan majalisar na  Waren ba su yi tunanin cewa ya kamata ya tsaya takara a zaben 2020 ba.
Kashi hamsin da takwas na masu jefa kuri'a na Massachusetts sun ce bai kamata sanata ya tsaya takara ba, a cewar binciken Cibiyar Binciken Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk/Boston Globe.
Kashi talatin da biyu cikin dari sun goyi bayan batun zaben.
Binciken ya nuna goyon baya ga ficewar zaben daga tsohon Gwamna Deval Patrick, inda kashi 38 cikin 100 suka goyi bayan ficewar zaben mai yiwuwa da kashi 48 cikin 100 suka ki.
Sauran manyan sunayen 'yan Democrat da aka tattauna dangane da yiwuwar fitowa zaben 2020 sun hada da tsohon mataimakin shugaban kasa Joe Biden da Sanata Bernie Sanders na Vermont.
