Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, a ranar Laraba, ya yi magana game da biyan kudin da ake biyan China Daily a Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa - bayan da ya zargi China da neman tsoma baki a zaben 'yan majalisar dokokin Amurka na ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
