An sake jinkirta sabon yakin Jamus
Sabon jirgin ruwan na rundunar sojin ruwan Jamus ya kamata a fara aiki a 2014 domin maye gurbin jiragen ruwan Cold War da ke aiki a yanzu, amma ba za a samu ba har sai a kalla shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma karuwar kudin, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na kasar.
An dage fara aikin Rheinland-Pfalz, babban jirgin ruwan sabbin jiragen ruwa masu karfin gaske na Baden-Wuerttemberg, zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019, a cewar jaridar Die Zeit da ke ambaton mai magana da yawun sojin.
An shirya jirgin ya shiga cikin rundunar sojin ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma matsalolin da suka taso bayan isar da sakon sun sa aikin ya zama mai wuyar aiwatarwa.
Jirgin ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg da aka ba da umarni a cikin 2007 za su maye gurbin jiragen ruwa na Bremen da ke aiki a cikin jirgin.
An fahimci cewa za su sami babban makami mai linzami, da makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami da kuma wasu fasahohi na tsaro, kamar su rage radar, infrared da siginar sauti.
Sauran mahimman ayyuka sun haɗa da tsawon lokutan kulawa - wannan ya kamata ya yiwu don aiki da sabbin firiji har zuwa shekaru biyu  nesa da tashoshin gida.
Duk da haka, jinkiri na ci gaba yana nufin cewa jiragen ruwa na zamani - waɗanda aka ambata sun ba Jamus damar tsara ƙarfin da ba ta so - za su riga sun zama tsoho lokacin da suka shiga sabis, Die Zeit ta lura.
Frigate F125 ta yi rashin sa'a ta zama sanarwa a shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da rundunar sojin ruwan Jamus ta ƙi ba da izinin fara aiki da jirgin kuma ta mayar da shi tashar jirgin ruwa ta Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne lokaci na farko da rundunar ta mayar da jirgin ruwa ga wani mai gina jirgi bayan ya kai shi.
An san kadan game da dalilan hakan, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambata wasu 'yan nakasa a cikin software da kayan aiki wadanda suka sanya jirgin kasa mara amfani idan aka tura shi kan aikin yaki.
Rashin inganci a cikin software ya kasance mai mahimmanci musamman tunda jirgin Baden-Wuerttemberg zai yi aiki da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa  kimanin 120 - rabin ma'aikata ne kawai a kan tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Bugu da ƙari, jirgin ya bayyana cewa yana da nauyi mai yawa wanda zai rage aikinsa kuma ya iyakance ikon Rundunar Sojan Ruwa don ƙara haɓaka nan gaba.
Jirgin Rhineland-Palatinate mai nauyin tan 7000 an fahimci cewa ya ninka na jiragen ruwa masu nauyin nau'in  da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a yakin duniya na biyu.
Baya ga rashin ingantattun kayan aiki, farashin duk aikin - gami da horar da ma'aikatan jirgin - yana zama matsala.
An ce wannan ya kai adadin  €3.1bn ($3.6bn) - daga €2.2bn na farko.
Matsalolin sabbin jiragen ruwa sun zama masu mahimmanci musamman a cikin hasken recentwararrun cewa ƙarfin jirgin ruwan Jamus yana raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaron majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya yarda cewa rundunar sojin ruwa a halin yanzu tana da karancin jiragen ruwa da za su iya jurewa.
Jami'in ya ce matsalar ta karu ne a tsawon lokaci, saboda an fara aiki da tsoffin jiragen ruwa amma ba a samar da wasu jiragen ruwa na maye gurbin ba.
Ya yi korafin cewa babu ɗayan jirgi na Baden-Wuerttemberg da za a iya haɗa shi da rundunar sojan ruwa.
