Za a iya sake jinkirta taron Trump da Rosenstein, in ji Fadar White House
Za a iya jinkirta ganawar Donald Trump da mataimakin babban lauya Rod Rosenstein har zuwa mako guda yayin da ake ci gaba da gwagwarmayar neman nadin Brett Kavanaugh a kotun koli, Fadar White House ta ce a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein na kula da aikin mai ba da shawara na musamman Robert Mueller, wanda ke binciken tsoma bakin Rasha a zaben, alakar masu taimakon Trump da Rasha da kuma yiwuwar cikas ga shari'a daga shugaban.
Ko Trump zai kori mataimakin babban lauya, ta haka ya yi barazana ga 'yancin Mueller, ya yi wa Washington ido na watanni.
A farkon wannan watan, jaridar New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya tattauna batun saka waya don yin rikodin tattaunawar da Trump da kuma yiwuwar kawar da shugaban kasa ta hanyar gyara 25.
Rosenstein ya musanta rahoton.
Amma a ranar Litinin da ta gabata ya je fadar White House, duk da cewa akwai rahotanni cewa zai yi murabus.
Maimakon haka, ta sanar da wani taro da Trump, wanda a lokacin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ke New York, wanda aka tsara don Alhamis.
Trump ya ce zai fi son kada a kori Rosenstein amma sai aka dage taron don kaucewa rikicin da ya faru a zaman kotun majalisa na majalisar dattawa wanda ya hada da Kavanaugh da daya daga cikin matan da suka zarge shi da laifin lalata, Dr Christine Blasey Ford, wadanda su biyu suka bayar da shaida.
A ranar Juma'a, Trump ya umarci FBI da ta gudanar da bincike kan zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh na tsawon mako guda, wanda ya dauki tsawon tsawon lokacin da za a kada kuri'ar da za a yi a majalisar dattawa.
A ranar Lahadi ne sakataren yada labaran Trump, Sarah Sanders, ta bayyana a Fox News.
Lokacin da aka tambaye ta game da taron Rosenstein, ta ce: "Ba a kafa kwanan wata ba tukuna, ana iya yin sa a wannan makon, kuma ana iya yin sa a mako mai zuwa saboda duk sauran abubuwan da ke gudana a kotun koli.
Amma yanzu mun gani kuma ina son in ci gaba da sabunta hoton.
Wasu 'yan jarida sun kalubalanci wannan ikirarin: Sanders ba ta shirya taron manema labarai a Fadar White House ba tun ranar 10 ga watan Satumba.
Mai gabatar da shirin Chris Wallace ya tambaye ni dalilin da ya sa.
Sanders ta ce rashin halartar tarurrukan ba saboda rashin jinƙai da 'yan jaridar talabijin ke yi ba ne, ko da yake ta ce: "Ko da yake na yarda cewa suna ƙoƙarin jawo hankalin masu sauraro".
Ta kuma ba da shawarar cewa za a kara samun hulda kai tsaye tsakanin Trump da manema labarai.
Shugaban ya yi tambayoyi da amsoshi fiye da kowane shugaban da ya taɓa halarta, ta kara da cewa ba tare da ambaton wata hujja ba: Ku duba waɗannan lambobin.
Za a ci gaba da yin taro, in ji Sanders, amma idan 'yan jarida suka samu damar yin tambayoyi ga shugaban Amurka kai tsaye, zai fi kyau su yi magana da ni.
Muna kokarin yin hakan sosai kuma mun ga muna yin hakan sau da yawa a cikin 'yan makonnin nan kuma wannan zai maye gurbin taron manema labarai inda za a iya yin magana da shugaban Amurka.
Trump ba safai yake amsa tambayoyi ba lokacin da yake barin fadar White House ko kuma lokacin da yake halartar taron jama'a ko kuma taron manema labarai lokacin da yake ziyartar manyan mutane.
Taron manema labarai na mutum ba safai ake yi ba.
A wannan makon a New York shugaban ya nuna dalilin da ya sa yake nuna halin rashin natsuwa da kuma wani lokacin rashin natsuwa a gaban 'yan jarida.
