Harris ya kara da cewa "a yanzu babu wani bayani kan irin/iyakar cutar" kuma Jihar Tennessee na kokarin gano lokacin da cutar ta faru.
Abercrombie, dan shekara biyu da aka dakatar, yana kakar wasa ta farko a jihar Tennessee bayan barin Illinois.
