Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa garin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, jami'ai sun ce, ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Tare da lalacewar hanyoyin sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun wani bayani daga yankin Donggala ba, wanda yanki ne a arewacin Palu wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5.
A Pallu, sama da mutane 16,000 ne aka kwashe bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, game da tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, wanda ke kan iyakar bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan mutane kusan 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekara 40 da kafuwarsa.
Donggala yanki ne da ya kai tsawon kilomita 300 (180 mil) na gabar tekun a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin 2017, yankin yana da yawan mutane 299,200.
Kifi da noma sune ginshikan tattalin arzikin lardin  Central Sulawesi, musamman yankin  Donggala na bakin teku.
Ma'adinan nickel ma yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma ya fi mayar da hankali a Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia, Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da girgizar kasa sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
A shekarar 1996, tsunami ya kuma afkawa yammacin Donggala, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana kan Ring of Fire na Pacific na girgizar kasa kuma tana yawan fuskantar girgizar ƙasa.
Waɗannan su ne wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, wata babbar girgizar kasa a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra ta haifar da wata tsunami da ta afkawa kasashe 14, inda ta kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa gaɓar yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 6.8 ta afkawa Kudu Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami mai ƙarfi a gabar tekun Kudu, wanda ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.6 ta afkawa kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta afkawa ɗaya daga cikin tsibirin Mentawai, a wajen Sumatra, ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa yankin  Pidie Jaya dake Aceh, inda ta haifar da bala'i da fargaba yayin da mutane ke tunawa da mummunan girgizar kasa da tsunami da suka faru a shekarar 2004.
Ba a yi wata annobar tsunami ba, amma an kashe mutane fiye da 100 a wurin.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar kasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a cikin wani yanayi na wucin gadi.
