Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya na neman a bai wa wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addancin birnin New York hukuncin kisa na musamman.
Masu gabatar da kara a New York suna neman a yanke wa Sayfullo Saipov wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci da ya kashe mutane takwas hukuncin kisa - hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa a jihar ba tun shekarar 1953 saboda wani laifi na tarayya.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi zargin cewa ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda a watan Oktoba ya yi wa masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu hawan keke da suka yi hijira a hanyarsa barazana.
Don a tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya yi kisan gilla ga wadanda aka kashe da kuma cewa ya yi mummunan rauni, a cewar sanarwar da aka gabatar a yankin kudancin New York.
A cewar takardar kotun, wadannan shugabannin biyu na tuhumar sun yi alkawarin hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, wata kotun tarayya ta yanke wa Saipov hukuncin daurin shekaru 22 da suka hada da tuhumar kisa guda takwas da taimakon kungiyar ta'addanci, wanda ake amfani da shi a matsayin hanyar da masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da ita wajen aikata laifuka, da kuma na tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Da suke kwatanta yadda Saipov ya kai harin ainihi, da zalunci da rashin mutunci, masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci shiryawa da tunani sosai.
Sanarwar ta bayyana cewa Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco rauni, lalacewa, da kuma asarar rayuka.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda suka mutu 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma sun shige tun da aka yi shari'ar kisa a gundumar Kudancin New York.
An samu wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da laifin kashe masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi guda biyu amma daga karshe a watan Satumbar 2009 aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka yanke hukuncin kisa a wata shari'ar tarayya ta New York ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an same su da laifin laifin da ake yi na yi wa Tarayyar Soviet leken asiri a lokacin Yakin Cold shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
