Dundee Stars sun sha wahala sakamakon rashin nasarar da suka yi a gasar Elite League ta mako da Belfast Giants, inda suka ci wasan da suka yi da su 5-3 a Dundee a ranar Asabar.
Giants sun sami nasara da kwallaye biyu a farkon wasan tare da hare-haren biyu daga Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun samu maki iri daya a wasan da suka buga a kasarsu kafin Dwyer ya sake samun damar cin nasara a kan Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya ci wa Dundee kwallo guda kafin kwallo biyu da Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya ci ya tabbatar da nasarar da suka samu.
Wannan shi ne nasara ta uku a kakar wasa ta Elite League ga 'yan wasan Adam Keefe, wanda bayan da suka sha kaye suka ci Dundee 2-1 a Belfast ranar Juma'a da yamma.
Wannan shi ne karo na hudu a kakar wasa da wadannan kungiyoyin biyu suka kara, yayin da Giants suka lashe wasannin uku da suka gabata.
Dwyer ya fara zura kwallo a minti na hudu da 3:35 da Kendall McFaull, tare da David Rutherford ya ci gaba da zura kwallo yayin da Beauvillier ya ninka ragamar bayan minti hudu.
A lokacin da aka fara wasan, Sullivan ya dawo da 'yan wasan gida a 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya yi wa Cownie wasa a 15:16 inda ya daidaita duka biyu.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da cewa Giants sun sami nasara har zuwa farkon wasan lokacin da ya zira kwallaye na biyu na dare a ƙarshen farkon.
Kungiyar da ke wasa a kasarsa ta sake haduwa kuma da taimakon Bouchard suka sake buga wa tawagarsa kwallo mai karfi a 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun hada gwiwa don taimakawa Nielsen ya baiwa Dundee damar cin nasara a karon farko a wasan a karshen karo na biyu kuma ya tabbatar da nasara da kwallaye biyar ga tawagarsa a tsakiyar karshe.
Giants, wadanda yanzu suka yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu daga cikin biyar da suka gabata, za su buga wasansu na gaba a ranar Juma'a a gida da Milton Keynes.
