Sabuntawar Red Tide: Abubuwan da ke raguwa a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Rahoton da ya fi kwanan nan daga Hukumar Kula da Kifin Kifin Florida ya nuna raguwar yawan Red Tide a sassan Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, ana samun rahoton yanayin yawan alkali a yankuna masu keɓewa a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier - wanda ke nuna raguwar taro.
Red Tide wanda shine ƙarancin algae yana da nisan mil 130 na gabar teku daga gefen Pinellas zuwa ƙasashen gefen Lee.
Za a iya samun yankunan da ke keɓewa mil 10 daga gabar tekun Hillsborough County, amma a wurare da yawa da suka shafi makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da Red Tide a Pasco County.
An samu matsakaitan maida hankali a bakin teku ko kuma a gefen tekun na Pinellas County a cikin makon da ya gabata, low zuwa high maida hankali a bakin teku na Hillsborough County, babban maida hankali a Manatee County, babban maida hankali a bakin teku ko kuma a gefen tekun na Sarasota County, matsakaicin maida hankali a Charlotte County, babban maida hankali a bakin teku ko kuma a gefen tekun na Lee County, da kuma ƙananan maida hankali a cikin County na Collier.
Ana ci gaba da bayar da rahoton tashin hankula a cikin Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da kuma Collier County.
Babu wani tashin hankali na numfashi da aka ruwaito a Arewa maso Yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
